<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-72-0537 </DOCNO><TEXT>A training simulator imitating the Heysham-2 NPP operation with the AGRtype reactor is briefly described. The simulator duplicates completelythe operator room, which comprises two instrument benches (active andpassive ones), operator control board, auxiliary facility, reactor shut-downmonitor and a number of electric panels. The simulator imitates the workof reactor and associated systems both in normal and accidental conditions.</TEXT></DOC>